## Immediate Priority Actions (Before Anything Else)

> [!WARNING]
> These three items must be fixed before any feature work proceeds.

1. **Verify dashboard auth** — Check if `/api/admin-dashboard`, `/api/owner-dashboard`, `/api/manager-dashboard` route handlers enforce `requireAuth` internally. If not, add `requireAuth` middleware in `server.js` on lines 239-243 immediately.

2. **Add private channel membership check to socket join** — Without this, any authenticated user can eavesdrop on private channel socket rooms.

3. **Add authorization to `huddle:join`** — Without this, any authenticated socket can join any huddle room.

